#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/close_tickets.rst:32
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, check the box labeled, :guilabel:`Folded in Kanban`, "
"towards the top of the window. Then, click :guilabel:`Save & Close` to "
